  <h2>🧬 Introduction</h2>
  <p>NeoShade AI is not a startup. It’s a soulstack. We’re building an unshakable legacy system for the next generation — one that preserves truth, respects sovereignty, and integrates ethical AI with decentralized systems. Our mission is to awaken minds, outlast manipulation, and safeguard memory in an age of distortion.</p>

  <h2>🧱 Core Pillars</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>NeoLegacy</strong>: AI-powered voice/video memory vaults for loved ones (Beta in 3–6 months)</li>
    <li><strong>Truth Terminal</strong>: Scriptural, philosophical, and historical dialogue AI</li>
    <li><strong>NeoAI Token ($NEOAI)</strong>: Utility for access, droid permissions, and decentralized voting</li>
    <li><strong>Swarm Apps</strong>: 9 Beta dApps already live, powering finance, data, insight, and interaction</li>
  </ul>

