  <h2>🔄 Firebase Architecture Notes</h2>
  <h3>❗ Concern:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Media storage costs grow rapidly at scale</li>
    <li>Realtime sync becomes expensive with traffic</li>
    <li>Centralized control undermines sovereign mission</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>🔁 Migration Plan:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ <strong>Arweave</strong> for permanent, immutable storage</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>IPFS</strong> for distributed access and archiving</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Supabase/Auth.js</strong> for open authentication</li>
  </ul>
  <blockquote>“Firebase was our rocket booster — but we’re landing this on Arweave armor and sovereign soil.”</blockquote>

